SUMMARY:Garden to Table - Super Green Salad
DESCRIPTION:Garden to Table \nMondays\, 4:00 PM – 5:00 PM \nMarch 2 – Super Green Salad \nThis month’s Garden to Table is all about the color green! Create your own salad recipe using all different greens\, and pairing with a gorgeous green salad dressing. \nEnjoy quality time in the garden with your child/children as we explore the Edible Garden and all that it has to offer. Help us weed and water\, plant\, and harvest. We will prepare a simple snack with ingredients inspired by the garden. Appropriate for children ages 4 and up but all are welcome. Children must be accompanied by an adult. \nSponsored by  \nFee: $15/class per child for Members / $20/class per child for General Public \nRegistration required by 1 day prior to each class
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/garden-to-table-super-green-salad/
LOCATION:Van Vleck House & Gardens\, 21 Van Vleck Street\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes,Children
