DTSTART:20260302T233000Z
DTEND:20260303T004500Z
DTSTAMP:20260302T000000Z
SUMMARY:Practical French I
DESCRIPTION:\nThis is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nGet a step-by-step approach to speaking and writing French 
 based on the way people naturally acquire language. Achieve grammar mastery 
 and gain confidence in your conversation skills even if you’re an 
 absolute beginner. This class is for students who have never taken French 
 or who took it many years ago in school.\n
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Conference Room\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Language
UID:LibCal-10306-15819763
URL:https://bccls.libcal.com/event/15819763
END:VEVENT
