SUMMARY:Poetry Writing Workshop
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nCome and write: In these two creative writing sessions\, we 
 will study poems and share lively conversation\, motivation\, strategies\, 
 writing prompts\, and feedback. This will be oriented toward writing 
 poems\, but may invite other possibilities as well.\n\n\nCome ready to play 
 and experiment with language & ideas. Bring an open heart\, an open mind\, 
 your adventurous spirit\, and whatever you like to write with: pencil and 
 paper\, laptop\, or phone.\n\nAll levels of experience welcome.
LOCATION:Montclair Bellevue Ave Branch - First Floor\, Montclair Bellevue Avenue Branch
