SUMMARY:Advanced English to Speakers of Other Languages (ESOL) for Professionals
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nAdvanced ESL is for Individuals who want to build confidence 
 in their English proficiency skills and communicate with clarity\, 
 directness\, and the cultural sensitivity expected in a professional 
 organization setting. The course includes vocabulary-building activities 
 with a focus on higher level-appropriate\, key academic\, and 
 high-frequency vocabulary\, as well as listening\, speaking  and writing 
 exercises to build confidence and competence among the American English 
 speaking community. Prerequisite: Intermediate English fluency is 
 required\, this is not a beginner's class.\n
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School
UID:LibCal-10306-15816362
URL:https://bccls.libcal.com/event/15816362
