SUMMARY:Heather Zises Book Talk
DESCRIPTION:In celebration of Women’s History Month\, Woman’s Club of Upper Montclair member Heather Zises will present a talk on her award-winning book\, 50 Contemporary Women Artists. The publication takes a pluralistic approach\, highlighting women artists and architects whose groundbreaking contributions have shaped contemporary art.\n$5 at the door. Open to the public. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/heather-zises-book-talk/
