SUMMARY:Hope is the Strategy Jen Fisher Book Launch at Loopwell
DESCRIPTION:Join Loopwell for an intimate evening with Jen Fisher\, celebrating her new book Hope Is the Strategy. Through science-backed research and personal storytelling\, Jen reframes hope as a measurable leadership skill that helps prevent burnout and build resilient\, thriving workplaces.\nDiscover practical tools for cultivating hope in yourself and your organization\, explore the neuroscience behind wellbeing at work\, and join an honest conversation about redesigning systems that support people\, purpose\, and performance. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/hope-is-the-strategy-jen-fisher-book-launch-at-loopwell/
LOCATION:Loopwell\, 80 Maple Ave\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:General Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Jen-Fisher.jpg
END:VEVENT
