SUMMARY:Beginner Mah Jongg - Thursday Afternoons in February - BAB
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nLooking for more fun in your life? Need an excuse to see your 
 friends without eating? Worried about dementia? Learn how to play the 
 ancient Chinese game of Mah Jongg! This game is not hard to play but 
 complex to learn. Our instructor's method of teaching is guaranteed to have 
 you playing with strategy by the end of the session.  This class will 
 prepare you for both online and in-person games.
LOCATION:Montclair Bellevue Ave Branch - Classroom\, Montclair Public Library
