SUMMARY:Black Women in Biopic: Harriet (2019)
DESCRIPTION:Harriet (2019) | PG-13\, 125mins\n\nThe incredible true story 
 of one of America's greatest heroes\, Harriet Tubman. From her escape from 
 slavery to the dangerous missions she led\, setting free hundreds of slaves 
 through the Underground Railroad. Watch the trailer here.\n\n\nSeating for 
 the film is first come\, first served. No registration is required.
