SUMMARY:Passaic Watershed Series: Great Falls\, Goffle\, and More!
DESCRIPTION:Metrotrails: NJ\, PA\, NY Metropolitan Area Hiking and More!\n
 Join us for this point to point hike in our Passaic River Watershed series
 \, this time leading us along a tributary known as the Goffle Brook\, whic
 h has some great trails along it\, as well as on back streets and through 
 parks along the river itself. Featured will be the Great Falls National Hi
 storic Site and some of the historic structures around it.\nWe'll continue
  to the west through the city and visit other small parks\, probably get s
 ome food\, and head to West Falls.\nDistance will be about 15 miles. If ne
 eded\, contact me at 908 343 8374
