SUMMARY:Basic Italian 1 - Online
DESCRIPTION:Note: This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to register 
 on the Adult School website. \n\n\nLearn to communicate effectively in 
 Italian in everyday situations through interactive lessons while enriching 
 your understanding and appreciation of Italian culture. This course is for 
 beginners and those who need a review of basic grammar\, everyday 
 expressions and essential vocabulary.  It is also appropriate for speakers 
 of other Romance languages who want to learn Italian easily and quickly.\n
