DESCRIPTION:Love graphics novels or interested in reading more? Join us for 
 our 18  Graphic Novel Book Club! We'll explore a new graphic novel every 
 month to read together and then meet to discussed the book. This book club 
 is exclusive for those 18 or older\, as some materials may contain content 
 not suitable for younger audiences.\n\n \n\nBook: Simplicity: A Novel by 
