X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Montclair Foundation": "https://montclairfoundation.org/event/tales-on-the-trails-seed-starting/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:montclairfoundation_calendar_of_events
X-SOURCE:Montclair Foundation
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260311T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260311T134500
DTSTAMP:20260301T222716
CREATED:20251216T153051Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260116T203656Z
UID:10005986-1773234000-1773236700@montclairfoundation.org
SUMMARY:Tales on the Trails - Seed Starting
DESCRIPTION:Tales on the Trails \nWednesdays\, 1:00 PM -1:45 PM \nAge: Preschool 3-5 year olds \nMarch 11th – Seed Starting \nSpring is right around the corner\, which means it’s time to start thinking about what to plant in your garden.  \nDiscover the wonders of the outdoor world with your little one.  This program begins in the gardens of Van Vleck with a story\, then continues with a walk and concludes with a simple craft or activity.  All programs focus on the theme listed.  A parent or caregiver must accompany each child.  Programs will be held outdoors\, weather permitting. \nSponsored by The Albert Payson Terhune Foundation  \nFee: $10/class per child for Members / $15/class per child for General Public \nRegistration required by 1 day prior to each class \n \n  \nUpcoming Classes \nApril 8th – Beauty of Trees \nApril’s Tales on the Trails class is all about trees. Learn about trees\, their leaves\, and the important role they play in our gardens. \n  \nMay 27th – Sounds of Spring \nDo you hear the birds singing\, the wind blowing\, and rabbits scurrying around? These are all the sounds of spring. Join us for Tales on the Trails as we use our senses to explore the wonders of spring. \n  \nJune 17th – Magic of Moths \nWhat’s flying around the gardens? Is it a butterfly or could it be a moth? Learn about moths at this month’s Tales on the Trails. 
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/tales-on-the-trails-seed-starting/
LOCATION:Van Vleck House & Gardens\, 21 Van Vleck Street\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes,Children
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairfoundation.org/content/uploads/2022/03/seeds-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
