SUMMARY:Social Worker Office Hours
DESCRIPTION:Margarette (they/them) can assist you with a variety of 
 services. See below for details. \n\nAppointments 11:15 a.m.\, 12:15 p.m.\, 
 1:15 p.m.\n\nSome of the services Margarette provides to the 
 community:\n\n\n	Connecting you with supportive services such as\, 
 housing\, healthcare\, mental health\, legal aid\, & food 
 support.\n	Assisting you in accessing unemployment\, Social Security\, 
 Medicare\, & other government assistance programs.\n	Equipping you with 
 tools and guidance for job searches\, resume building\, and navigating 
 college & job applications.\n
