SUMMARY:Afternoon Storytime (birth-5 years)
DESCRIPTION:Come join us for an afternoon storytime for ages birth-5. We 
 will read stories\, sing songs\, and move about.We might even dance a 
 little! Storytime will be downstairs at the Bellevue Avenue Branch\, Kids 
 Place. If weather permits\, storytime will take place outside\, please 
 bring a blanket to sit on. No registration required.\n\nTo stay informed\, 
 sign up for one or all of our eNewsletters\, click here.
