 se contributions to contemporary music.\nConcert fearturing Montclair Sta
 te University Faculty\, students and a special guest The Rhythm Method Qu
 artet\nThe Rhythm Method is a quartet of composer-performers reimagining 
 the string quartet through a contemporary\, intersectional feminist lens—
 collaborating closely with composers\, blending improvisation and notatio
 n\, amplifying marginalized voices\, and fostering collective creativity 
 through performance and education.\nAll are welcome. Reservations are not
  necessary.\n\nHosted by: The College of the Arts\n\nAdditional Informati
 on can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/1229047
