SUMMARY:Play-Doh Playdate (ages 2-5)
DESCRIPTION:This hands-on program invites children to explore their 
 creativity and fine motor skills through free play with Play-Doh. Children 
 will engage in sensory exploration\, shaping\, and molding while learning 
 about textures and colors. No registration required\; space is limited.\n\n
