 h the American Red Cross and help make a life-saving impact. Whether you’
 re a first-time donor or a seasoned pro\, your donation can help replenis
 h critical blood supplies used in emergencies\, surgeries\, and more. It’
 s quick\, easy\, and one of the most meaningful ways to give back to your
  community.\nSo roll up your sleeve\, grab a friend\, and join us in turn
 ing compassion into action—because every drop counts. Snacks\, smiles\, a
 nd gratitude await! \nRSVPing on Engage does not mean you are registered 
