 his project provides hands-on guidance\, practical resources\, and person
 alized feedback to help students confidently present their skills\, exper
 iences\, and achievements. There will be snacks provided!\n\nHosted by: B
 loomfield Lambda Theta Alpha Latin Sorority\, Inc.\, Bloomfield Lambda Si
 gma Upsilon Latino Fraternity\, Inc.\n\nAdditional Information can be fou
 nd at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12264005
