 ther.\nWe're hosting a virtual information session on March 19 at 6:00 PM
 . This is a no-pressure\, exploratory space to meet our team and determin
 e if our program fits your goals.\nOur coursework offers a broad focus on
  administration and leadership\, preparing students for a variety of role
 s in higher education. The curriculum integrates organizational and socia
 l science perspectives and explores key administrative and programmatic i
