BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Montclair State University": "https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12228722"}
X-SOURCE-ID:montclair_engage_events_ics
X-SOURCE:Montclair State University
CATEGORIES:Arts
DESCRIPTION:Masterclass with Kyle Resnick\nFree and Open to the Public\, R
 eservations not Required\nJoin the brass area for a very special mastercl
 ass with trumpeter Kyle Resnick. Kyle will work with Cali students and sh
 are what he's learned on his incredible musical journey that has seen him
  performing and recording with Taylor Swift\, Ed Sheeran\, Bruce Springst
 een\, Beirut\, The National\, and Mumford and Sons\, among others!\nBio:\
 nKyle Resnick is a trumpet player known for his versatility and contribut
 ions to both live performances and studio recordings across a wide variet
 y of genres and musical styles. He has established himself as a prominent
  figure in the music industry through collaborations with a diverse array
  of artists and groups\, from recording for Taylor Swift (“Folklore\,” “E
 vermore\,” and “Midnights”)\, Ed Sheeran and Bruce Springsteen\, among se
 veral others\, to Classical chamber and solo and countless orchestral per
 formances on concert stages over three decades. He has felt equally at ho
 me on stages like Carnegie Hall\, Lincoln Center\, the Barbican\, Royal A
 lbert Hall\, Sydney Opera House and venues such as the Hollywood Bowl\, a
 nd arenas and stadiums around the globe. Kyle is a longstanding touring a
 nd recording member of the bands The National and Beirut\, and has commen
 ced in 2025 on a world tour with the band Mumford & Sons\, for which he h
 as also recorded on the last two albums. Since his time as a student to t
 he present day\, Kyle has found great satisfaction enriching his musical 
 journey through teaching trumpet and directing ensembles\, having served 
 on the faculties of Juilliard Pre-College\, Brooklyn College\, SUNY Unive
 rsity at Buffalo and SUNY Buffalo State.\n\nHosted by: The College of the
  Arts\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://montclair.campus
 labs.com/engage/event/12228722
DTEND:20260320T190000Z
DTSTAMP:20260302T033127Z
DTSTART:20260320T180000Z
GEO:40.858180;-74.199730
LOCATION:Leshowitz Recital Hall
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:CALI SCHOOL OF MUSiC |  Masterclass with Kyle Resnick
UID:https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12228722
URL:https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12228722
X-HOSTS:The College of the Arts
END:VEVENT
