X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Montclair Foundation": "https://montclairfoundation.org/event/monday-morning-yoga-hybrid-in-person-virtual-12-6/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:montclairfoundation_calendar_of_events
X-SOURCE:Montclair Foundation
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260323T093000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260323T104500
DTSTAMP:20260301T222716
CREATED:20260217T161515Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260226T184416Z
UID:10006174-1774258200-1774262700@montclairfoundation.org
SUMMARY:Monday Morning Yoga - HYBRID in-person / virtual
DESCRIPTION:Early Spring Session: March 2\, 9\, 16\, 23\, 30\, April 6\, 13\, 20\, 27 \nMondays\, 9:30 AM – 10:45 AM \nInstructor: Jennifer Hondru-Celestin \nJoin our welcoming community for a meditative yoga flow practice in the Van Vleck living room overlooking the charming courtyard gardens. All levels of yoga experience are welcome in this dynamic\, inclusive class. Our teacher Jennifer Hondru-Celestin takes inspiration from the natural beauty around us to flow with the seasons\, blending mindful movement\, breath\, meditation\, and a good dose of humor and fun.  This class welcomes all levels from beginner to experienced yogis. Bring your own yoga mat and props. \nFee:  Single class: $23 Members / $28 Non-Members \nSeries (9 classes): $180 members and $225 general public
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/monday-morning-yoga-hybrid-in-person-virtual-12-6/
LOCATION:Van Vleck House & Gardens\, 21 Van Vleck Street\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes,Adults,Virtual
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairfoundation.org/content/uploads/2026/01/Yoga-Group-Indoors-2.jpg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Montclair Foundation": "https://montclairfoundation.org/event/journaling-in-the-garden/2026-03-23/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:montclairfoundation_calendar_of_events
X-SOURCE:Montclair Foundation
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260323T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260323T130000
DTSTAMP:20260301T222716
CREATED:20260204T161342Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260204T161558Z
UID:10006608-1774267200-1774270800@montclairfoundation.org
SUMMARY:Journaling in the Garden
DESCRIPTION:Journaling in the Garden \nMonthly on Mondays\, 12:00 PM – 1:00 PM. (Series or individual Classes) \nMarch 23rd \nApril 13th \nMay 11th \nJune 15th \nExplore the beauty of the Van Vleck Gardens this spring through reflective writing and creative mark-making.  This mindfulness-based class/series invites you to slow down\, observe the natural world and turn your blank pages into a wonderland of personal observations.  Each class takes place in a different area of the Gardens (weather permitting)\, offering new inspiration for discovery.  Deepen your connection with nature and yourself in a no-pressure environment.  No art or writing experience necessary – just an openness to explore\, reflect and create.   \nFee: Series Rate (4 classes): $50 Members / $70 General Public \nIndividual Rate: $15 Members / $20 General Public \nRegistration required by 1 day prior to class.
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/journaling-in-the-garden/2026-03-23/
LOCATION:Van Vleck House & Gardens\, 21 Van Vleck Street\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes,Adults
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairfoundation.org/content/uploads/2026/01/nature-journaling-1-e1768316290510.jpg
END:VEVENT
