 lls\, and gain a deeper understanding of what it means to be a lifelong m
 ember of the organization. NME meetings create a supportive environment w
 here new members can ask questions\, reflect on their experiences\, and p
 repare for initiation while strengthening their sense of belonging within
  the chapter.\n\nHosted by: Sigma Sigma Sigma\n\nAdditional Information c
 an be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12251779
