DESCRIPTION:Registration Open NJ Real Estate Broker 30-Hour Ethics/Agency 
 Course March 24th - April 8th 5:30pm - 9:30pm Burgos Realty Academy offers
  the 30-hour Ethics and Agency Broker course as part of New Jersey?s requi
 red 150-hour Broker pre-licensing curriculum. This instructor-led program 
 supports broker candidates by strengthening ethical judgment\, agency rela
 tionships\, and supervisory responsibilities. The full 150-hour Broker pre
 -licensing requirement includes: 30 Hours – Ethics & Agency 30 Hours –
  Office Management 90 Hours – Basic Broker Courses are taught by a licen
 sed broker-owner\, real estate instructor and ARELLO Certified Distance Ed
 ucation Instructor. Courses are designed to prepare students not only for 
 the broker exam\, but for leadership and operational success in today?s re
 al estate industry.
