DESCRIPTION:Are you a junior or senior interested in graduate school\, res
 earch\, public service\, or international experiences? The Prestigious Sc
 holarships Program is here to support you! A prestigious scholarship prov
 ides you with the opportunity to develop your skills and reach your goals
  through engagement with people and places around the world. Montclair’s 
 Prestigious Scholarships Program helps all students and alumni learn of a
 nd apply for nationally and internationally competitive and prestigious a
 wards. These awards fund a wide range of opportunities\, as well as indep
 endent research projects\, and many are connected to undergraduate and gr
 aduate degree programs or internships around the globe.\n\nHosted by: Pre
 stigious Scholarships \n\nOnline Location: https://montclair.zoom.us/j/92
 277903565?pwd=Tca0PyYSoHaXaJC2ojOHr4kb6vdYJS.1&jst=2 \n\nAdditional Infor
 mation can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/122
 34706
